sql: SELECT c.cmi_cross_ref_id FROM Benefits_Overpayments AS c JOIN Benefits_Overpayments ON Benefits_Overpayments.council_tax_id = c.council_tax_id
SELECT AVG(s.electoral_register_id), s.cmi_cross_ref_id FROM Electoral_Register AS s WHERE s.electoral_register_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  s.cmi_cross_ref_id >= 13 LIMIT 10

SELECT source_system_code FROM CMI_Cross_References JOIN Benefits_Overpayments JOIN Customer_Master_Index ON CMI_Cross_References.master_customer_id = Customer_Master_Index.master_customer_id AND Benefits_Overpayments.cmi_cross_ref_id = CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id WHERE CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  Benefits_Overpayments.cmi_cross_ref_id < 58 LIMIT 7
SELECT MAX(cmi_cross_ref_id), cmi_cross_ref_id, council_tax_id FROM Benefits_Overpayments WHERE  cmi_cross_ref_id > 53 GROUP BY cmi_cross_ref_id

SELECT MAX(Rent_Arrears.cmi_cross_ref_id), COUNT(DISTINCT source_system_code), Council_Tax.cmi_cross_ref_id FROM CMI_Cross_References JOIN Council_Tax JOIN Customer_Master_Index JOIN Rent_Arrears ON CMI_Cross_References.master_customer_id = Customer_Master_Index.master_customer_id AND Council_Tax.cmi_cross_ref_id = CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id AND Rent_Arrears.cmi_cross_ref_id = CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id WHERE  CMI_Cross_References.master_customer_id >= 17 AND council_tax_id >= (SELECT AVG(council_tax_id) FROM Parking_Fines AS x) GROUP BY Council_Tax.cmi_cross_ref_id ORDER BY Council_Tax.cmi_cross_ref_id ASC

SELECT Council_Tax.cmi_cross_ref_id FROM Council_Tax JOIN CMI_Cross_References ON Council_Tax.cmi_cross_ref_id = CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id WHERE master_customer_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR cmi_cross_ref_id IN (SELECT cmi_cross_ref_id FROM Rent_Arrears)

SELECT Business_Rates.business_rates_id, q.cmi_cross_ref_id FROM Business_Rates AS q JOIN Business_Rates ON Business_Rates.business_rates_id = q.business_rates_id WHERE  q.business_rates_id = 51 GROUP BY q.cmi_cross_ref_id LIMIT 9
SELECT cmi_cross_ref_id, council_tax_id FROM Benefits_Overpayments WHERE  cmi_cross_ref_id = 53

SELECT council_tax_id, source_system_code FROM CMI_Cross_References JOIN Council_Tax JOIN Electoral_Register JOIN Customer_Master_Index ON CMI_Cross_References.master_customer_id = Customer_Master_Index.master_customer_id AND CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id = Electoral_Register.cmi_cross_ref_id AND Council_Tax.cmi_cross_ref_id = CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id WHERE  Customer_Master_Index.master_customer_id < 50 LIMIT 1

SELECT source_system_code, source_system_code, source_system_code FROM CMI_Cross_References JOIN Benefits_Overpayments ON Benefits_Overpayments.cmi_cross_ref_id = CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id WHERE council_tax_id = (SELECT MIN(council_tax_id) FROM Rent_Arrears) GROUP BY source_system_code LIMIT 9

SELECT Benefits_Overpayments.cmi_cross_ref_id FROM CMI_Cross_References JOIN Benefits_Overpayments JOIN Electoral_Register ON CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id = Electoral_Register.cmi_cross_ref_id AND Benefits_Overpayments.cmi_cross_ref_id = CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id WHERE  council_tax_id <= 73 ORDER BY Benefits_Overpayments.cmi_cross_ref_id ASC
SELECT AVG(m.council_tax_id), m.council_tax_id, m.cmi_cross_ref_id FROM Rent_Arrears AS m WHERE m.cmi_cross_ref_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  m.cmi_cross_ref_id >= 39 GROUP BY m.cmi_cross_ref_id

SELECT source_system_code FROM Council_Tax JOIN Benefits_Overpayments JOIN CMI_Cross_References JOIN Rent_Arrears ON Council_Tax.cmi_cross_ref_id = CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id AND Benefits_Overpayments.cmi_cross_ref_id = CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id AND Rent_Arrears.cmi_cross_ref_id = CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT x.cmi_details), Customer_Master_Index.cmi_details FROM Customer_Master_Index AS x JOIN Customer_Master_Index ON Customer_Master_Index.master_customer_id = x.master_customer_id ORDER BY Customer_Master_Index.cmi_details DESC

SELECT source_system_code, source_system_code, Rent_Arrears.cmi_cross_ref_id FROM CMI_Cross_References JOIN Benefits_Overpayments JOIN Rent_Arrears ON Benefits_Overpayments.cmi_cross_ref_id = CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id AND Rent_Arrears.cmi_cross_ref_id = CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id WHERE  Benefits_Overpayments.cmi_cross_ref_id <= 91 GROUP BY Rent_Arrears.cmi_cross_ref_id LIMIT 5

SELECT AVG(Rent_Arrears.cmi_cross_ref_id), COUNT(DISTINCT t.cmi_cross_ref_id) FROM Rent_Arrears AS t JOIN Rent_Arrears ON Rent_Arrears.council_tax_id = t.council_tax_id WHERE  t.cmi_cross_ref_id >= 25

SELECT e.master_customer_id, e.cmi_details FROM Customer_Master_Index AS e WHERE e.master_customer_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  e.master_customer_id <= 66 GROUP BY e.cmi_details HAVING SUM(e.master_customer_id) >= 6 LIMIT 3

SELECT COUNT(electoral_register_id), COUNT(DISTINCT electoral_register_id), cmi_cross_ref_id FROM Electoral_Register WHERE  electoral_register_id <= 95 AND electoral_register_id <= (SELECT MIN(electoral_register_id) FROM Electoral_Register WHERE  electoral_register_id <= 2 LIMIT 1) GROUP BY cmi_cross_ref_id HAVING MIN(cmi_cross_ref_id) < 8 ORDER BY cmi_cross_ref_id DESC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Benefits_Overpayments.council_tax_id), y.cmi_cross_ref_id FROM Benefits_Overpayments AS y JOIN Benefits_Overpayments ON Benefits_Overpayments.council_tax_id = y.council_tax_id WHERE  y.council_tax_id <= 44 GROUP BY y.cmi_cross_ref_id HAVING SUM(Benefits_Overpayments.cmi_cross_ref_id) >= 34 ORDER BY y.cmi_cross_ref_id ASC LIMIT 5

SELECT Benefits_Overpayments.cmi_cross_ref_id, source_system_code FROM CMI_Cross_References JOIN Benefits_Overpayments ON Benefits_Overpayments.cmi_cross_ref_id = CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id WHERE  master_customer_id = 88 AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM Rent_Arrears AS x WHERE  x.cmi_cross_ref_id >= 50 AND CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id = x.cmi_cross_ref_id) GROUP BY source_system_code
SELECT cmi_cross_ref_id FROM Electoral_Register WHERE EXISTS (SELECT * FROM CMI_Cross_References AS w WHERE Electoral_Register.electoral_register_id = w.cmi_cross_ref_id)

SELECT council_tax_id, source_system_code FROM CMI_Cross_References JOIN Benefits_Overpayments ON Benefits_Overpayments.cmi_cross_ref_id = CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id WHERE  CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id > 69
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT master_customer_id), master_customer_id FROM Customer_Master_Index WHERE  master_customer_id != 68 LIMIT 3

SELECT CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id, source_system_code FROM CMI_Cross_References JOIN Electoral_Register ON CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id = Electoral_Register.cmi_cross_ref_id WHERE  master_customer_id < 29

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id), cmi_details FROM CMI_Cross_References JOIN Council_Tax JOIN Customer_Master_Index ON CMI_Cross_References.master_customer_id = Customer_Master_Index.master_customer_id AND Council_Tax.cmi_cross_ref_id = CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id WHERE  Council_Tax.cmi_cross_ref_id <= 63 OR EXISTS (SELECT * FROM CMI_Cross_References WHERE Council_Tax.council_tax_id = cmi_cross_ref_id) GROUP BY cmi_details

SELECT COUNT(council_tax_id), source_system_code, source_system_code FROM CMI_Cross_References JOIN Electoral_Register JOIN Rent_Arrears ON CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id = Electoral_Register.cmi_cross_ref_id AND Rent_Arrears.cmi_cross_ref_id = CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id WHERE EXISTS (SELECT * FROM CMI_Cross_References WHERE Rent_Arrears.council_tax_id = cmi_cross_ref_id LIMIT 8)

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT CMI_Cross_References.master_customer_id), COUNT(DISTINCT cmi_cross_ref_id), source_system_code FROM CMI_Cross_References JOIN Customer_Master_Index ON CMI_Cross_References.master_customer_id = Customer_Master_Index.master_customer_id WHERE  cmi_cross_ref_id <= 11
